title: Italy's voters reject the mainstream
text:
Italy's voters reject the mainstream 9:10pm GMT - 02:01 
The anti-establishment 5-Star Movement and the far-right League emerged as the biggest winners from Italy's election, following an inconclusive poll likely to create political instability in the eurozone's third biggest economy. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
